headline: ICE First Look at Mortgage Performance: Increased Refinance Activity Drives Mortgage Prepayments to 3.5-Year High
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, November 25, 2025--ICE Mortgage Technology, a neutral provider of a robust end-to-end mortgage platform and part of Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), today released the October 2025 ICE First Look at mortgage delinquency, foreclosure and prepayment trends.
